- Mom?
- <i>by the effects of Oscar</i>
<i>and Lucille's Afternoon Deelite.</i>

19:04.476 --> 19:07.968
- Tobias-Tobias, watch out.
- <i>[Narrator] Tobias couldn't hear</i>- 

