19:40.312 --> 19:43.213
- [Engine Revving]
- I got you, Brother!

19:45.651 --> 19:47.676
[Giddy Laughter]

19:50.822 --> 19:52.915
[Onlookers Laughing]

19:53.025 --> 19:55.994
<i>[Narrator] And for the second time</i>
<i>since he became president...</i>

19:56.094 --> 19:58.858
<i>Gob heard the sweet sound</i>
<i>oflaughter.</i>

19:58.964 --> 20:04.698
They're laughing with me, Michael.
They're laughing with me!

20:04.803 --> 20:08.136
<i>[Narrator] Unfortunately,</i>
<i>Buster's newfound skills...</i>

20:08.240 --> 20:12.233
<i>did not involve</i>
<i>lowering gently.</i>

20:12.344 --> 20:15.438
- <i>[Onlookers] Ooh. Oh.</i>
- <i>[Splash]</i>

20:18.317 --> 20:22.549
<i>Hey, it's Tobias.</i>
<i>Who wants to take me to the hospital?</i>

20:22.654 --> 20:25.248
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>And so father and son reunited...</i>

20:25.357 --> 20:28.292
<i>rebuilding the banana stand</i>
<i>for a second time.</i>

20:28.393 --> 20:31.453
- Hey. Can I give you a hand?
- <i>Hey. Yeah.</i>

20:31.563 --> 20:35.397
- That would be great.
- Okay.

20:35.500 --> 20:39.869
- Oh, I'm sorry about-
It's embarrassing, the whole-
- Listen, I, uh-

20:39.972 --> 20:42.304
I've been a little out of line lately.
You're entitled...

20:42.407 --> 20:44.841
to be with your girlfriend,
and I guess I got a little bit jealous.

20:44.943 --> 20:47.912
- Yeah. Well, me too.
- Yeah.

20:48.013 --> 20:50.709
Okay.

